column2: SELECT TOP #      sp.bestObjID AS sdssid_SpecObjAll,   sp.ra AS RA_sdss,   sp.dec AS DEC_sdss,   sp.z AS zsp,   sp.zErr AS e_zsp,   sp.class AS class,   sp.subClass AS subClass,   sp.zWarning AS zWarning,      phz.objID AS sdssid_Photoz,   phz.z AS zph,   phz.zErr AS e_zph,      ph.objID AS sdssid,   ph.ra AS RA_sdss,   ph.dec AS DEC_sdss,   ph.mode AS mode,   ph.probPSF AS probPSF,  propability that object is the star    ph.modelMag_u AS umag,   ph.modelMag_g AS gmag,   ph.modelMag_r AS rmag,   ph.modelMag_i AS imag,   ph.modelMag_z AS zmag,   ph.modelMagErr_u AS e_umag,   ph.modelMagErr_g AS e_gmag,   ph.modelMagErr_r AS e_rmag,   ph.modelMagErr_i AS e_imag,   ph.modelMagErr_z AS e_zmag,      gsl.SpecObjId AS sdssid,   gsi.z	AS z,			   gsi.z_err AS zErr,				   gsi.z_warning AS zWarning,   gsi.reliable AS reliable_line_measure,      gsl.nii_#_flux AS NII_#_FLUX,   gsl.sii_#_flux AS SII_#_FLUX,   gsl.oi_#_flux AS OI_#_FLUX,   gsl.oiii_#_flux AS OIII_#_FLUX,   gsl.h_alpha_flux AS H_ALPHA_FLUX,   gsl.h_beta_flux AS H_BETA_FLUX,      gsl.nii_#_flux_err AS NII_#_flux_err,   gsl.sii_#_flux_err AS SII_#_flux_err,   gsl.oi_#_flux_err AS OI_#_flux_err,   gsl.oiii_#_flux_err AS OIII_#_flux_err,   gsl.h_alpha_flux_err AS H_ALPHA_flux_err,   gsl.h_beta_flux_err AS H_BETA_flux_err     FROM   SpecObjAll AS sp,   Photoz AS phz,   PhotoObjAll AS ph,   galSpecLine AS gsl,   galSpecInfo AS gsi       WHERE   sp.bestObjID = phz.objID   AND phz.objID = ph.objID   AND ph.objID = gsl.SpecObjId   AND gsl.SpecObjId = gsi.SpecObjId
